+frameInbox('What gamers want')
	div
		ul
			li.fragment <span class="highlight-2 italic">Most gamers don't know what they want until it is shown to them.</span> <span class="highlight-2">(Scott Rogers)</span>
			li.fragment a good game is a unique way of structuring experience and provoking emotions
			li.fragment most successful games are addictive and mood-boosting
			li.fragment gamers enjoy failing, as long as hope of success is at hand
			li.fragment <span class="highlight-2">the destiny of all games is to eventually become boring</span>
			li.mt-80.fragment <span class="highlight">Essential rewards to gameplay</span>
				ul
