		ul
			li.fragment(data-fragment-index='1') game design is a highly iterative process
			li.fragment(data-fragment-index='2') <span class="highlight">conceptualize</span> - develop an idea and its play experience - written in design document
			li.fragment(data-fragment-index='3') <span class="highlight">prototype</span> - make some aspect of the game's design into a playable form
			li.fragment(data-fragment-index='4') <span class="highlight">playtest</span> - have the players see what you have made
			li.fragment(data-fragment-index='5') <span class="highlight">evaluation</span> - capture feedback, take notes, videos, brainstorm, and start another iteration
