					li.fragment How did they solve the design problems? 
					li.fragment Look for existing patterns
			li.fragment Get to prototyping!
			li.fragment Show it to people, get feedback.
			li.fragment Iterate until you get to the "sweet spot"
			li.fragment Don't be afraid to fail
			li.fragment Practice your design skills
